{"tid":505412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[你講中左］華湧：如果講真話就係英雄，中國係幾撚可怕","createTime":"2017-12-21T05:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T06:08:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f949a74a1344aab8e81b7c7ed48851ab36ebac84","tid":505412,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/133944_31c7991c24939bfaf29ba1a598be4ab4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F133944_31c7991c24939bfaf29ba1a598be4ab4.jpg&h=1a5c71c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實錄「低端人口」慘況後被捕　華湧獲釋堅稱自己非英雄：我只是拍個真話 (22:36) - 20171220 - 兩岸<br />\n<br />\n內地藝術家華湧實錄北京「低端人口」慘況後被捕，星期一獲釋取保候審。網上有片段見華湧抱着女兒吃飯，席間他澄清自己不是英雄：「如果說真話就變英雄，中國得多可怕啊。」<br />\n<br />\ntwitter流傳一席影片，相信是華湧獲釋後與親友吃飯時拍下。他抱着女兒發言，語氣頗激動：「我英雄個屁啊？我就是拍個真話，老太太說啥我就拍了&hellip;&hellip;如果說真話就變英雄了，中國得多可怕啊！」另有一段影片，則是華湧感謝友人關心，惟強調自己生活沒問題，不會接受捐款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171220/s00004/1513780571108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171220%2Fs00004%2F1513780571108&d=pDKrl1Vp8gUPhiduO97o%2F%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=acd91107\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171220%2Fs00004%2F1513780571108&h=971be639\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171220/s00004/1513780571108</a>"},{"pid":"3c7991e155d1ac23fbe19db2224fb85791065eea","tid":505412,"uid":44646,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/133944_31c7991c24939bfaf29ba1a598be4ab4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F133944_31c7991c24939bfaf29ba1a598be4ab4.jpg&h=1a5c71c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實錄「低端人口」慘況後被捕　華湧獲釋堅稱自己非英雄：我只是拍個真話 (22:36) - 20171220 - 兩岸<br />\n<br />\n內地藝術家華湧實錄北京「低端人口」慘況後被捕，星期一獲釋取保候審。網上有片段見華湧抱着女兒吃飯，席間他澄清自己不是英雄：「如果說真話就變英雄，中國得多可怕啊。」<br />\n<br />\ntwitter流傳一席影片，相信是華湧獲釋後與親友吃飯時拍下。他抱着女兒發言，語氣頗激動：「我英雄個屁啊？我就是拍個真話，老太太說啥我就拍了&hellip;&hellip;如果說真話就變英雄了，中國得多可怕啊！」另有一段影片，則是華湧感謝友人關心，惟強調自己生活沒問題，不會接受捐款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171220/s00004/1513780571108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171220%2Fs00004%2F1513780571108&d=pDKrl1Vp8gUPhiduO97o%2F%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=acd91107\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171220%2Fs00004%2F1513780571108&h=971be639\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171220/s00004/1513780571108</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真話成為英雄不算最可怕--起碼有人在道德上認同你。<br />\n<br />\n更可怕係講完真話，犧牲完，之後連回音都無一聲。"},{"pid":"19aafde04ac32172c3debce3b6e4f860cea4c4b7","tid":505412,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:56:17.000Z","msg":"某d國家講話會冇命架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你夠膽講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb6e3c94c88631ff1601186e5cc775151916da2","tid":505412,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:57:44.000Z","msg":"事實就係咁可怕"},{"pid":"42bb922147eb32347f2cee8180ad1a87686a2166","tid":505412,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:01:35.000Z","msg":"佢太天真啦，平民心中仍然有一絲良知，講真話才能成為英雄"},{"pid":"be717761d84046f29fac62abfbb9f52c53172ad4","tid":505412,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06955e647bfe55d44f77770af5e42dbb13bf5924","tid":505412,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"蚛蟈人根本無得救"},{"pid":"f816310a2c4b28e47b1dcca38d23b38f41f27946","tid":505412,"uid":42588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"梗係唔好認自己係英雄，喺強國做英雄多數都無好下場。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}